items.name: Cardi B SDXL LoRA
items.description:
Thank you to razzz for the tip on training to 800mb!

14400 steps. Yep this one was a big one. Trained in local Kohya install. 4090. Trained on DreamShaper XL1.0 Alpha2. I followed SECourses SDXL LoRA Guide.

This model was testing a couple of things. One being the larger training image dataset, hence the larger amount of steps. Two being, yes, a non-1.7GB LoRA. Only future tests/outputs/comparisons will tell if there is a quality loss in this or not. I decided to scale down the size per high demand and preliminary speculation based on observations that hopefully it wont diminish the overall quality of the model. Worth noting if you are also training SDXL LoRAs yourself that this method of training to achieve 800mb files also lowers your overall GPU VRAM usage from ~18gb to ~15gb.

Most images were on DreamShaper XL A2 in A1111/ComfyUI. Hi-res fix with R-ESRGAN (1.25) and 0.2-0.4 denoising strength. Upscaled using "4x_NickelbackFS_72000_G" or "4x_NMKD-Siax_200k"

Help me out by liking and following me to see my new models. Submit some of your outputs and post your SUGGESTIONS in the comments below. I am pacing around 6-10 models weekly depending on my actual job workload. If you liked my models and want to support the work I do you can buy me a pizza!

List of upcoming LoRAs I intend to do as well as what I am currently working on.

Thank you to razzz for the tip on training to 800mb!

items.name: Hyper-sensitive photography: LoRA Based on X-ray Features
items.description:
English/中文

This LoRA model takes inspiration from transparent textured photos generated by X-ray radiography. It learns the unique texture and applies color processing to ultimately not only have the ability to directly generate X-ray radiographs but also generate colored photographs with the distinctive transparent texture of X-ray radiographs.

Instructions:

  • Transparent Photography: Generates photographs with a unique transparent texture. Adding "skeleton" can generate characters with transparent skin. To achieve better color effects, you can add the negative word "monochrome," but there is a chance it may generate an oil painting style.

  • X-ray Films: "skeleton" plus "black background" or "white background".

  • Trigger word: xc

  • Weight: 0.8-1

  • Example image generation parameters: Steps: 20, Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras, CFG scale: 7, Size: 512x768, Denoising strength: 0.5, Clip skip: 2, Hires upscale: 2, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+.

  • Recommended positive prompts: innocent, shadow, fantasy, dream, masterpiece, highres, best quality, highly detailed. I also encourage everyone to share their own images and explore various effects generated by different prompts! (Caution: X-ray images should be used with care, and some specific actions may not accurately generate results.)

Note:

  1. This LoRA model is a mixture of multiple concepts, which inevitably leads to some elements being overfitted. When undesired elements appear, you can add corresponding elements in the negative terms to resolve them, for example: curly hair, navel, headband, sunglasses, text, etc.

  2. Please use negative embeddings like "bad-hands" and "easynegative" with caution as they may affect the image generation results.

  3. Due to limitations in the dataset, generating animal or fictional creature skeletons may be inaccurate and may result in the generation of animal heads with human bodies or human heads with animal bodies.(which maybe shouldn't be considered a drawback, haha)

  4. This LoRA is trained based on SD1.5, so it can be applied to most checkpoints based on SD1.5. There may be slight differences in the results generated by different models (some 2D models are also effective). Among the three large models I tested, I recommend using "cyberrealistic_v31".

本LoRA以X线平片摄影产生的透明质感照片为灵感，学习其独有的特殊质感并加以色彩的加工，最终使其不仅具有直接生成X线平片的能力，同时也能够生成带有X线平片独特透明质感的彩色摄影图片。

使用方法：

  • 透明感摄影：可产生独特透明质感的摄影图片；加skeleton可以生成肌肤透明的人物；若想要更好的实现彩色效果，可添加负面词monochrome，但有概率会生成油画风格

  • X光片：skeleton加black background 或 white background

  • 必需触发词：xc

  • 权重：0.8-1

  • 例图生成参数：Steps: 20, Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras, CFG scale: 7, Size: 512x768, Denoising strength: 0.5, Clip skip: 2, Hires upscale: 2, Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+,

  • 推荐正面提示词：innocent,shadow,fantasy,dream,masterpiece,highres,best quality,highly detailed,也希望大家多多分享自己的图片、探索不同提示词产生的各式效果！(X光片图慎用，部分指定动作无法准确生成)

注意：

1.该LoRA由多种概念混合而成，不可避免的导致部分元素过拟合；当你不想要的元素出现时，可在负面词添加相应元素以解决，例如：curly hair,navel,headband,sunglasses,text等

2.请谨慎使用如bad-hands、easynegative等负面嵌入，它们可能会对图片生成效果产生影响

3.由于数据集限制，动物或虚拟生物骨骼生成会不准确，会有生成兽头人身的情况

4.该LoRA以SD1.5为底模训练，故可适用于大多数以SD1.5为基础的大模型，不同模型产生的效果会有少许差异(部分二次元模型也有效)。我测试的三个大模型中，推荐使用cyberrealistic_v31。

items.name: Pointing Meme SDXL
items.description:
❤ Please post any images made with this model here for further improvement of the dataset ❤

Prompt Format:

duo selfie pose, two <men/women/things> next to each other, a <thing> in the background

Optional tags include:

<happy/shocked/excited> expressions, open mouth, pointing to the side, selfie pose

Versions:

v14 (Recommended): U-Net only; Much more flexible prompting by training with a known similar concept (duo selfie pose).

v5 (Previously Recommended): U-Net only; Improved dataset captioning for more flexible prompting. It's still kind of finicky but it's an improvement.

v8e (Experimental): Text Encoder + U-Net; Trained for fewer steps with a higher weight decay (0.02). Adjust the individual weights of the Text Encoders and U-Net if you don't get the pointing.

v4: U-Net only; Initial release, tends to produce women wearing lots of neck jewelry

Prompting for older versions:

Prompt format:

two <men/women/things> pointing at <something>, the <man/woman/thing> on the right is pointing at <something>, the <man/woman/thing>on the left is surprised

If you're having trouble getting the arm to point, try adding tags like "pointing a finger", "fingerless gloves", etc.

items.name: Donald Trump Jr. - (HQ Dreambooth Trained)
items.description:
High Quality Dreambooth (JP's 24gb repo) trained checkpoint model of Donald Trump Jr created using hi-resolution images of the influencer from social media, cameo, and recent news media.

Why a full checkpoint/2GB model for 1 subject?

Simply because the trained checkpoint gives you the best quality to start w/. LoRAs are fantastic for lots of things, but for human likenesses they don't match up to Dreambooth trained checkpoints. I train with Dreambooth and then extract a LoRA from that if needed.


"I need a LoRA for my workflow!"

It's easy to extract a LoRA from an SD checkpoint on your own if you prefer a LoRA for your workflow. For instance you can use the Auto1111 extension "Supermerger" to extract a LoRA. That said, LoRA will not match the quality of the original Dreambooth model (loss incurred). Be nice, have fun!

Gary Leonard Oldman (born 21 March 1958) is an English actor and filmmaker. Known for his versatility and intense acting style, he has received various accolades, including an Academy Award, a Golden Globe Award, and three British Academy Film Awards. His films have grossed over $11 billion worldwide, making him one of the highest-grossing actors of all time.[1]

Oldman began acting in theatre in 1979 and made his film debut in Remembrance (1982). He continued to follow a stage career in London's Royal Court and was a member of the Royal Shakespeare Company, with credits including Cabaret, Romeo and Juliet, Entertaining Mr Sloane, Saved, The Country Wife and Hamlet. He rose to prominence in British film with his portrayals of Sid Vicious in Sid and Nancy (1986), Joe Orton in Prick Up Your Ears (1987) and Rosencrantz in Rosencrantz & Guildenstern Are Dead (1990), while also attracting attention as the leader of a gang of football hooligans in the television film The Firm (1989). Regarded as a member of the "Brit Pack",[2] he achieved greater recognition as a New York gangster in State of Grace (1990), Lee Harvey Oswald in JFK (1991) and Count Dracula in Bram Stoker's Dracula (1992).

Oldman portrayed the villains in films such as True Romance (1993), The Fifth Element (1997), Air Force One (1997) and The Contender (2000); corrupt DEA agent Norman Stansfield, whom he played in Léon: The Professional (1994), was called one of cinema's best villains. He also played Ludwig van Beethoven in Immortal Beloved (1994) and later appeared in franchise roles such as Sirius Black in the Harry Potter series, James Gordon in The Dark Knight Trilogy (2005–2012) and a human leader, Dreyfus in Dawn of the Planet of the Apes (2014). He won the Academy Award for Best Actor for his role as Winston Churchill in Darkest Hour (2017), and was nominated for his portrayals of George Smiley in Tinker Tailor Soldier Spy (2011) and Herman J. Mankiewicz in Mank (2020).

Oldman was executive producer of films like The Contender, Plunkett & Macleane (1999) and Nil by Mouth (1997), the latter of which he also wrote and directed. He has featured in television shows such as Slow Horses, Fallen Angels, Tracey Takes On... and Friends, voiced Ignitius and Viktor Reznov respectively in The Legend of Spyro and Call of Duty video games, and appeared in music videos for David Bowie, Guns N' Roses and Annie Lennox.

My first attempt at making LoRA's, So if its shit, I'm sorry.

Also, you might notice that some character are easier to reproduce than others you might notice that those harder to reproduce characters also appear less on screen, this is not coincidence.

items.name: 【再世】next life-欧阳佩珊（陈洁英）
items.description:
这是群星再世第六十九期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

欧阳佩珊，本名陈洁英，1970年，17岁的欧阳佩珊通过电影圈正式出道，五年后，她加入丽的电视，在此后的近二十年时间里，她的事业重心都投入到电视圈当中，在1978年到1989年这段时期，她是在TVB度过，她曾先后担任过汪明荃、赵雅芝、郑裕玲、陈玉莲等多位著名花旦的配角，而她出演主角的机会却寥寥无几，尽管如此，她所塑造的不少角色都可以称得上为永恒的经典。

80版《上海滩》是最早登陆内地的电视剧之一，该剧堪称TVB电视史上最为经典的民国剧，周润发、吕良伟、赵雅芝等主演因为该剧而红遍全国大江南北，欧阳佩珊在剧中饰演女特务山口香子一角，只有短短四集的戏份，因此她的名字也不被内地观众所熟知，然而她所塑造的角色却惊艳了无数内地观众，在后来网络兴起的时代，“《上海滩》女特务扮演者”也成为了网上的热搜。

这时候她已经是红透半边天了，可以说已经超过了很多的明星艺人，但就在90年代，欧阳佩珊开始第二次淡出影视界，在拍摄完《重案组》之后，就彻底退出了演艺界，去往了内地学习中医，并且跟随师父张仁峰教授学习气功，在学习毕业之后，还成为了一名执业气功针灸师。

2017年因肺腺癌去世，享年63岁。

整理素材的时候有古装有时装，全部都是年轻时的照片，没有她50岁之后的照片。

《千里江山图》是北宋王希孟创作的绢本设色画，现收藏于北京故宫博物院。研究指出，《千里江山图》的主要取景地是庐山和鄱阳湖。

千里江山图》画卷，不仅代表着青绿山水发展的里程；而且，集北宋以来水墨山水之大成， 并将创作者的情感付诸创作之中。《千里江山图》虽属于写意之作，但不乏工美佳作，表现了青年画家具有严谨的生活态度。《千里江山图》是中国十大传世名画之一。

A Thousand Miles of Rivers and Mountains" picture scroll not only represents the milestones in the development of green landscapes; Although "A Thousand Miles of Rivers and Mountains" is a freehand work, it is not lacking in exquisite workmanship, which shows the rigorous life attitude of the young painter. "A Thousand Miles of Rivers and Mountains" is one of the top ten famous paintings in China.
